Specimen Container(s): 6 mL LDPE vial with dispensing tip and cap
Instrument(s)/Platform(s): Blood glucose meters and test strips manufactured by TaiDoc Technology Corporation
Method(s)/Technology(ies): Enzymatic reaction using glucose oxidase or glucose dehydrogenase
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Glucose Meter-Check Solution for TaiDoc as an aqueous control solution for performance assessment of TaiDoc blood glucose meters and test strips
Indications for Use Summary: Intended for in vitro diagnostic use to assess the performance of blood glucose meters and test strips manufactured by TaiDoc Technology Corporation by healthcare professionals and home users with diabetes mellitus
